long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is Rate My Professors Extension for Davidson College course selection. Allowing you to view professor ratings by just highlight their name.

How to use:
1. Install the Google extension
2. Highlight the professor's name you wanna search
3. Click search button on the popup window
